
> SETUP CLOUD INSTANCE 
-- To set up Atlassian Cloud Instance, 
   1> Go to https://www.atlassian.com/ 
   2> Click on Get Started.
   3> Sign up
   4> Select Scrum (By default)
   5> Give Project Name and team name. 
   6> Click Ok.

> IF WE WANT TO CHANGE AND MANAGE PLANS 
-- 1> Go to settings
   2> Billing Preview
   3> Manage
   4> Choose the required plan 
   5> Click ok

